        <item>
            <title>【实试】SONY REON POCKET 5 穿戴式冷气，香港售价 + 1.5 倍冷却功率、更悭电</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/sony-reon-pocket-5-first-impression/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-reon-pocket-5-first-impression</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/sony-reon-pocket-5-first-impression/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 02:01:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[个人移动装置]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[运动科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY REON POCKET 5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[便携冷气]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1230702</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>好快就到夏天，出门口都想凉浸浸，你就需要一个智能手提冷气。今日 Sony 就正式发布了 Reon Pocket 5 便携冷气。新机冷却功率进一步升级，而且电池更加耐用，配合温度感应自动调节功能，以及一向 Reon Pocket 都有，在冬天专用的发热功能，这部新一代穿戴式便携冷气又真是几吸引。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0008-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0008-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0008.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230729" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0077-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0077-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0077.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0023-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0023-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0023-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>冷却功率为上代 1.5 倍、续航力为上代 1.8 倍</h2><p>SONY 官方公布 REON POCKET 5 穿戴式便携冷气。简单来说它是一个挂颈式装置，其传导片将冷感或热力传递到背部近颈部的皮肤。在夏天户外活动时，可给用户冰凉感觉，适合长期在户外活动的朋友。挂颈式装置亦可令用户的双手可用来做其他事，例如照顾小朋友或宠物。</p><h2>评测影片</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_66507"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/90on4cbkJFA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0028-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0028-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0028.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230703" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/img_8919-672x580.jpg" alt="" width="672" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/img_8919-672x580.jpg 672w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/img_8919.jpg 1042w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 672px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲官方数据展示最新一代 REON POCKET 5 在佩戴 5 分钟后，由于主机冷却功率更强，身体表面温度下降幅度更大</p><p>REON POCKET 5 具有上代 1.5 倍的冷却功率，带来更强吸热性能，而且电池使用时间最多长达上代 1.8 倍，更适合更长时间户外活动。unwire 记者水哥还有小编实际使用，发现冷气机变冷的速度相当快，很快就能为用户带来清凉快感。传导板的感觉就像一杯雪冻了的不锈钢杯杯面。上代清凉度分 1~4、4+ 级，而今代就新加入了 5、5+ 级清凉度，实际上都可感觉到今代 REON POCKET 5 金属片的制冷效果更强。用户可通过手机 App 调节清凉程度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230723" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0045-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0045-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0045.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>官方公布之使用时间</strong></p><p><strong>冷气模式</strong></p><p>等级 1：约 17 小时</p><p>等级 2：约 12 小时</p><p>等级 3：约 10 小时</p><p>等级 4：约 7.5 小时</p><p>等级 5：约 4 小时</p><p>等级 5+：需要连接外部电源才可使用</p><p><strong>暖气模式</strong></p><p>等级 1：约 8 小时</p><p>等级 2：约 6 小时</p><p>等级 3：约 5 小时</p><p>等级 4：约 4 小时</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230728" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0080-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0080-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0080.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230727" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0083-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0083-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0083.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲当你连接流动电源时，可选择最新的「5+」制冷模式，这个模式可说是马上制冷而且效能颇强</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230750" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/440018668_9924040392-1-694x396.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/440018668_9924040392-1-694x396.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/440018668_9924040392-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在 5 级冷却效能时，机身上方的噪音也仅在可轻微听到的范围</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230732" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0086-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0086-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0086.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在开启 5+ 急速制冷时，REON POCKET 就会发出较强噪音，但在户外（特别在城市环境）使用时被车声掩盖也不太听到</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230734" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0096-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0096-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0096.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在冷房或冬天时，可开暖气模式，REON POCKET 马上变暖蛋</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/sony-reon-pocket-5/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">SONY Reon Pocket 5  开箱评测影片，随身冷气</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>智能冷暖模式：结合主机、TAG 自动控制冷暖度</h2><p>而除了手动设定清凉度外，更可透过智能冷暖模式，从你的衣服内的热度与周边环境温度，智能设定清凉度。REON POCKET 5 套装跟来了 REON POCKET TAG 感应器，内置的感应器可传送环境温度、湿度到智能手机，配合 REON POCKET 在衣服里面的温度，自动设定最适合的清凉度。例如在室内环境中，室温大约为摄氏 25 度身体表面温度与衣服内温度较低，此时智能冷暖模式会设置为「微」；在阴天的户外环境中，智能模式可为你设置为「弱」。而在炎热的户外环境下再步行 10 分钟，你的皮肤与衣服内的温度会变得较高，REON POCKET 会自动调节到「强」制冷效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0035-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0035-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0035.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲REON POCKET TAG 感应器可令智能调节更加贴合当时温度</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230735" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0037-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0037-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0037.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲REON POCKET TAG 可独立使用或配合 REON POCKET 使用，在手机上可显示更准确的温度、湿度</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0007-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0007-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0007.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲SMART COOL WARM 智能冷暖模式可根据需要自动调节放冷、热</p><p>智能冷暖模式更可在制冷、制热功能间切换。例如你身处室内冷气较强的环境，可自动调节到 WARM MODE 放热模式，而当你走到户外，可自动切换到 COOL MODE 为你制冷。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0047-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0047-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0047.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家也可开启 SMART COOL 模式只让它制冷</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230726" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0054-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0054-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0054.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230725" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0052-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0052-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0052.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲REON POCKET 独立吹风模式，可以马上输出强风</p><h2>适合不同衣服、颈围用家</h2><p>REON POCKET 5 将备有两款排气口护盖，无论穿 T 裇或者领口较高的裇衫，都可令制冷／制热后的排气顺利从衣服排出。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230715" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0057-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0057-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0057.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0072-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0072-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0072.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>专用颈带内置有弹性机械管与金属线框，可随意扭曲令主机更能贴服你的颈部，防止你在户外走动时移位。外表的矽橡胶套可保持佩戴时的舒适感。附随的颈带适合 34mm 至 46mm 颈围的用家使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230731" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0073-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0073-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0073.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230730" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0064-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0064-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0064.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家可以扭曲颈带以调节颈带松紧度</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0027-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0027-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0027.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲颈围更细的用家，可选购「REON POCKET 专用颈带（小）」配件</p><h2>REON POCKET 5 产品系列售价与供应</h2><p>所有产品预售日期：2024 年 4 月 23 日</p><p>正式发售日期：2024 年 5 月 7 日</p><p>限时预购礼遇：购买 REON POCKET 5 套装 ($1,499) 送 REON POCKET 专用机套（原价$180）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230704" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/img_8929-694x368.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="368" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/img_8929-694x368.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/img_8929-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>REON POCKET 5 套装（型号：RNPK-5T）：包括 REON POCKET 5, TAG, 专用颈带、双排气口盖套装</p><p>售价：HK$1,499</p><p>REON POCKET TAG（型号：RNPT-1）</p><p>售价：HK$199</p><p>(可配合 REON POCKET 4, REON POCKET 5 两代主机使用）</p><p>REON POCKET 专用机套（型号：RNPC-1）</p><p>售价：HK$180</p><p>REON POCKET 专用颈带（型号：RNPB-N4）</p><p>售价：HK$149</p><p>REON POCKET 专用颈带（小）（型号：RNPB-N4s）</p><p>售价：HK$149</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/sony-reon-pocket-5/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">SONY Reon Pocket 5  开箱评测影片，随身冷气</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/sony-reon-pocket-5-first-impression/life-tech/">【实试】SONY REON POCKET 5 穿戴式冷气，香港售价 + 1.5 倍冷却功率、更悭电</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
